CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper April 21, 1956, pg. 30, reads: "Swim Winners - These members of the Centre YMCA swimming team show the results of good coaching and unusual ability.  Already this season they have shown well and served notice that they are to be reckoned with.  Left to right, Morris Fountain Jr. and Nat Clark, who set new meet marks; Roland [Ronald] Saunders, free-style winner, and Terence [Terrance] L. Gorman, coach. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Coach Terrance Gorman squatting on diving board with Morris Fountain Jr., Ronald "Ron" Saunders, and Nathan "Nat" Clark preparing to dive, at Centre Avenue YMCA indoor swimming pool
